<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 13:18:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>强大的人工智能使面部识别能够更好地识别您的身份</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/powerful-ai-is-making-facial-recognition-better-at-identifying-you</link><description>新的基于人工智能的面部识别技术正在减少误报和漏报匹配。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/powerful-ai-is-making-facial-recognition-better-at-identifying-you.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 13:18:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/powerful-ai-is-making-facial-recognition-better-at-identifying-you</guid></item><item><title>着丝粒在侵袭性癌症的端粒上留下足迹</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/centromeres-leave-footprints-on-telomeres-in-aggressive-cancers</link><description>研究人员发现，在端粒选择性延长（ALT）肿瘤中，着丝粒蛋白定位于端粒，从而提供了新的生物标志物靶点。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/centromeres-leave-footprints-on-telomeres-in-aggressive-cancers.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 13:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/centromeres-leave-footprints-on-telomeres-in-aggressive-cancers</guid></item><item><title>机器学习揭示了追踪阿拉斯加微板 250 公里边缘的 1,750 次地震</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/machine-learning-uncovers-1750-quakes-tracing-250-kilometer-edge-of-alaska-microplate</link><description>机器学习过程首次检测到数千次小地震，揭示了雅库塔特微板块俯冲到北美板块下方时独特、锋利的边缘。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/machine-learning-uncovers-1750-quakes-tracing-250-kilometer-edge-of-alaska-microplate.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 12:48:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/machine-learning-uncovers-1750-quakes-tracing-250-kilometer-edge-of-alaska-microplate</guid></item><item><title>美国实验室解开聚变等离子体之谜以保护反应堆热流</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/us-lab-untangles-fusion-plasma-mystery-to-protect-reactor-heat-flow</link><description>PPPL 研究人员已经确定了聚变等离子体产生自身强磁场的原因，为改进聚变反应堆设计提供了工具。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/us-lab-untangles-fusion-plasma-mystery-to-protect-reactor-heat-flow2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 12:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/us-lab-untangles-fusion-plasma-mystery-to-protect-reactor-heat-flow</guid></item><item><title>为什么古希腊美德“sophrosyne”在人工智能时代比以往任何时候都更加重要</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/why-sophrosyne-an-ancient-greek-virtue-matters-more-than-ever-in-the-age-of-ai</link><description>作为&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/why-sophrosyne-an-ancient-greek-virtue-matters-more-than-ever-in-the-age-of-ai.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 12:18:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/why-sophrosyne-an-ancient-greek-virtue-matters-more-than-ever-in-the-age-of-ai</guid></item><item><title>经过物理训练的数字“超级大脑”加速纳米光子设计</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/physics-trained-digital-super-brain-speeds-nanophotonic-design</link><description>研究物理学非常有用——即使涉及到机器学习。瑞典查尔姆斯理工大学的一项新研究表明，内置自然基本定律知识的数字“超级大脑”可以加快从量子计算机到眼镜或相机镜头等各种光学元件的开发。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/physics-trained-digital-super-brain-speeds-nanophotonic-design.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 12:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/physics-trained-digital-super-brain-speeds-nanophotonic-design</guid></item><item><title>星形胶质细胞可以在脑损伤后获得神经干细胞特性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/astrocytes-can-gain-neural-stem-cell-properties-after-brain-injury</link><description>新的研究表明，特定类型的脑细胞在脑损伤后变得活跃，并表现出与脑损伤相似的特性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/astrocytes-can-gain-neural-stem-cell-properties-after-brain-injury.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 11:48:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/astrocytes-can-gain-neural-stem-cell-properties-after-brain-injury</guid></item><item><title>飞越我们可观测宇宙中的每一个星系 — 太空纪录片 2026</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/flying-through-every-galaxy-in-our-observable-universe-space-documentary-2026</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 11:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/flying-through-every-galaxy-in-our-observable-universe-space-documentary-2026</guid></item><item><title>临床前测试中可注射水凝胶可缓解骨关节炎疼痛并修复软骨</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/injectable-hydrogel-relieves-osteoarthritis-pain-and-repairs-cartilage-in-preclinical-tests</link><description>对于数百万患有骨关节炎的人来说，日常生活可能会经历令人沮丧的疼痛和僵硬循环。虽然目前的治疗方法如非处方药或类固醇注射可以暂时减轻疼痛，但它们并不能阻止关节恶化。耶鲁大学的一项研究发表在期刊上&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/injectable-hydrogel-relieves-osteoarthritis-pain-and-repairs-cartilage-in-preclinical-tests3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 11:18:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/injectable-hydrogel-relieves-osteoarthritis-pain-and-repairs-cartilage-in-preclinical-tests</guid></item><item><title>大前庭神经鞘瘤位置对手术结果的放射学分析</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/radiologic-analysis-of-large-vestibular-schwannoma-position-on-surgical-outcomes</link><description>大型前庭神经鞘瘤 (VS) 通常会压迫脑干，并且与内耳道 (IAC) 的关系有所不同；这些放射学特征对术后结果的重要性仍不清楚。本研究量化了脑干受压 (BSC) 和相对于 IAC 的位置对 VS 手术结果的影响。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/radiologic-analysis-of-large-vestibular-schwannoma-position-on-surgical-outcomes.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 11:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/radiologic-analysis-of-large-vestibular-schwannoma-position-on-surgical-outcomes</guid></item></channel></rss>